<module>
    <h>dubh</h>
    <p><g>dubh</g>
        <adj/>
        <en>black</en></p>

    <section id="nouns">
        <h>nouns</h>
        <p><g><a href="?gd=cuu">cù</a> dubh</g>
            <en>a black dog</en> – <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>A bheil an cù dubh? Tha.</gd>
                    <tr>Is the dog black? Yes, it is.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 13</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Chan eil an cù dubh anns an achadh an diugh.</gd>
                    <tr>The black dog is not in the field today.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 14 [227]</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha cù dubh aig Calum ach tha cat bàn aig Seònaid.</gd>
                    <tr>Malcolm has a black dog but Janet has a white cat.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 23</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha cù mór dubh aig Calum ach tha cat beag bòidheach aig Màiri.</gd>
                    <tr>Malcolm has a big black dog but Mary has a pretty little cat.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 25</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>
        <p><g><a href="?gd=falt">falt</a> dubh</g>
            <en>black hair</en> – <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha falt dubh air Calum.</gd>
                    <tr>Calum has black hair.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 9 [adapted]</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>
        <p><g><a href="?gd=coota">còta</a> dubh</g>
            <en>a black coat</en> – <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha còta dubh air a’ chaileig seo ach ’s e còta dearg a tha air Màiri.</gd>
                    <tr>This girl has a black coat on but it’s a red coat that Mary has on.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 40</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>
    </section>






